{"name": "test_etcd_ha_failover_sglang_disaggregated", "status": "passed", "description": "\n    Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries in disaggregated mode using SGLang.\n\n    This test:\n    1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n    2. Starts NATS, frontend, and both prefill and decode SGLang workers\n    3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n       - Terminate the replica by index\n       - Send inference request to verify system still works\n       - Restart the terminated node\n\n    This ensures testing of:\n    - ETCD leader termination\n    - Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n\n    Note: This test requires 2 GPUs to run decode and prefill workers on separate GPUs.\n    ", "attachments": [{"name": "log", "source": "33b4219d-3f48-46b0-ab0a-4a4526641a95-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stdout", "source": "483a660e-afb7-49ac-af00-1bfbc19b8f45-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}, {"name": "stderr", "source": "16b99335-e362-4771-91e6-020169812513-attachment.txt", "type": "text/plain"}], "parameters": [{"name": "framework", "value": "'sglang'"}, {"name": "platform", "value": "'amd64'"}, {"name": "test_type", "value": "'pre_merge_gpu'"}], "start": 1775682767766, "stop": 1775682862001, "uuid": "5f153a34-49f0-43c1-954c-e3b7975f7a2b", "historyId": "d248dc1297013ab844a0d53e027efd2d", "testCaseId": "4e44a3af7724f4968ef83af169c82729", "fullName": "tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha.test_sglang#test_etcd_ha_failover_sglang_disaggregated", "labels": [{"name": "dynamo_workflow", "value": "Nightly CI Pipeline"}, {"name": "dynamo_framework", "value": "sglang"}, {"name": "dynamo_platform", "value": "amd64"}, {"name": "dynamo_testType", "value": "pre_merge_gpu"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "nightly"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "e2e"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "gpu_2"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "fault_tolerance"}, {"name": "tag", "value": "sglang"}, {"name": "parentSuite", "value": "tests.fault_tolerance